	* R/norMix.R (qnorMix): ditto
	* man/pnorMix.Rd: new

	* R/norMix.R (plot.norMix): default xout from xlim if that is given
	    now works with `log = "y"'.

	* man/norMix.Rd:  log = "y"

	* R/zzz.R (rmultinom): new; rmultinom() only for R <= 1.6

